    "hotelDescription": "Set in the Bruce Ridge Nature Reserve, this rural resort is 4 km from Australian National Botanic Gardens and 6 km from Australian War Memorial.\n Bright rooms have Wi-Fi access and flat-screen TVs, plus minifridges, microwaves, and tea and coffeemaking equipment. Upgraded rooms and cabins, some with bunk beds, add kitchenettes. Modern 2- to 3-bedroom cottages come with decks and living rooms.\n Parking is complimentary. There’s a casual, airy cafe/bar. Other amenities include an outdoor pool and a playground, as well as tennis, basketball and volleyball courts. A BBQ area and guest laundry facilities are offered. A campsite is also available.",
